highlights.text: “Bam Bam” by Banfy and Sheridan is the highest new entry on Top Songs Italy at #146.
“Destri” by Gazzelle has been on Top Songs Italy the longest, at 951 days straight.
Sfera Ebbasta has the most spots on Top Songs Italy. “Yakuza” is the highest at #5.
“All The Stars (with SZA) - From "Black Panther: The Album"” by Kendrick Lamar and SZA is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Italy, up 36 spots at #130.
